snippet.title: Does Amber Heard Have Borderline Personality Disorder? (Trigger Warning!)
snippet.description:
This is my personal Youtube channel, where I'll share podcasts, vlogs, rants, and other miscellaneous videos. This is not only to educate people and spark discussion about mental health but I created this Youtube to bring awareness to society and also as a way not to lose my head.

*Disclaimer: If you have BPD, please know that I believe not all Borderlines are the same and that no matter what/if Amber Heard truly does suffer from a mental health disorder, she is an extreme case of an untreated abuser.

In tonight's podcast, I am discussing Amber Heard showing characteristics of BPD.

Full audio here: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=aca0KWoHtqQ

#Justice4JohnnyDepp • #BPD • #AmberHeard
